---
import Layout from '../../layouts/bot.astro';
---

<Layout title="bot">
	<main>
		<h2>
			<div class="content">
        		<div class="roundThing2"></div>
				<div class="texts">
					rocks - my awesome bot - it might do somthing cool eventually, who knows?
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content2">
				currently my bot lacks a lot of any functionality and is just a very generic discord bot. It probably wont be online
				half the time either, thats because i dont have a host yet but i plan to get a raspberry pi soon enough. Anyway enjoy!
				<h2>the commands are:</h2>
				<div class="drink">
					<ul>
						<li><h3>/ping</h3></li>
						<li><h3>/usr</h3></li>
						<li><h3>/server</h3></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				anyway It will probably be receiving updates soon<br>
				and you can invite it to your discord server <a href="https://discord.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=1213580875124572230&permissions=8&scope=bot">here.</a>
			</div>
		</h2>
	</main>
</Layout>
<style>
	ul {
    	list-style-type:disc;
		color: white;
    	margin: 0%;
		margin-left: 5%;
